00:00:34.610 --> 00:00:39.020
dedicated to the prevention of
genocide and mass atrocities

00:00:39.020 --> 00:00:40.520
worldwide.

00:00:40.520 --> 00:00:47.030
Subsequently, in 2015, she
became global mentor for peace

00:00:47.030 --> 00:00:49.220
at Serve to Unite,
an organization that

00:00:49.220 --> 00:00:52.970
cultivates peace through
creative service learning

00:00:52.970 --> 00:00:55.070
and a global engagement.

00:00:55.070 --> 00:00:57.260
Dydine is committed
to establishing

00:00:57.260 --> 00:01:00.350
a dialogue between
people for understanding

00:01:00.350 --> 00:01:03.530
their shared histories
and cultural differences.

00:01:03.530 --> 00:01:05.630
Through her writing
and public lectures,

00:01:05.630 --> 00:01:10.730
her goal is to pierce the
wall of silence that still

00:01:10.730 --> 00:01:13.010
pervades much of our society.

00:01:13.010 --> 00:01:16.133
Please join me in
welcoming Dydine Umunyana.

