00:44:50.700 --> 00:44:53.970
he was really aggressive,
really aggressive.

00:44:53.970 --> 00:44:55.140
I got scared.

00:44:55.140 --> 00:44:57.430
And then he could talk,
like, really talk.

00:44:57.430 --> 00:44:59.670
And he was like, yes, I am.

00:44:59.670 --> 00:45:03.000
And I was like, how about
children who are Muslim?

00:45:03.000 --> 00:45:04.470
And he said, you never know.

00:45:04.470 --> 00:45:06.764
You never know what
those kids have!

00:45:06.764 --> 00:45:07.940
And I said, why?

00:45:07.940 --> 00:45:08.870
In those dresses!

00:45:08.870 --> 00:45:10.490
And I said, what do you mean?

00:45:10.490 --> 00:45:13.420
He's like, maybe they have
something, a bomb or anything.

00:45:13.420 --> 00:45:17.440
So then he became the
person that he is.

00:45:17.440 --> 00:45:19.920
But when he was
learning how to reform,

00:45:19.920 --> 00:45:22.560
when he was trying to be
a nice person in front

00:45:22.560 --> 00:45:27.130
of a black girl, he was
really quiet and shy,

00:45:27.130 --> 00:45:30.102
and he would even cry
because he told me

00:45:30.102 --> 00:45:31.560
it was the first
time he's ever sat

00:45:31.560 --> 00:45:35.060
across the table
with a black person.

00:45:35.060 --> 00:45:39.420
And I think if we
can be able to switch

00:45:39.420 --> 00:45:45.060
that, he can use that strength,
and that strength in him that

00:45:45.060 --> 00:45:48.810
comes out when he thinks about
what he hates so much, to use

00:45:48.810 --> 00:45:51.580
it when he's thinking
about why he loves so much.

00:45:51.580 --> 00:45:55.050
And I think we all
have that capacity

00:45:55.050 --> 00:45:57.105
because we grow what we feed.

00:45:57.105 --> 00:45:59.700
We have those two
sides in ourselves,

00:45:59.700 --> 00:46:04.920
and if we feed more light
in us, it really comes out.

00:46:04.920 --> 00:46:08.040
Because I used to
not be this girl.

00:46:08.040 --> 00:46:12.696
I used to be angry all the time
to everyone and everything.

00:46:12.696 --> 00:46:14.306
Are you shocked?

00:46:14.306 --> 00:46:17.655
AUDIENCE: Yeah, it's hard to
