something, they may shy away.

00:47:06.300 --> 00:47:08.090
But I think that's
what we learn.

00:47:08.090 --> 00:47:11.640
So we can really be able
to teach how to be excited

00:47:11.640 --> 00:47:15.030
when something
wonderful is happening,

00:47:15.030 --> 00:47:18.420
or we've done
something wonderful,

00:47:18.420 --> 00:47:22.662
then we can make him change
the way we see life and--

00:47:22.662 --> 00:47:23.870
yeah.

