still during the genocide.

00:52:22.160 --> 00:52:24.760
But after, there was
a lot of non-profits

00:52:24.760 --> 00:52:26.620
that came into Rwanda.

00:52:26.620 --> 00:52:32.795
So it's a very, very
vague situation.

00:52:32.795 --> 00:52:37.450
