control those kinds of minds

00:53:20.280 --> 00:53:24.230
that are completely--

00:53:24.230 --> 00:53:27.550
yeah, I don't know how to--

00:53:27.550 --> 00:53:28.800
SPEAKER: No, it's complicated.

00:53:28.800 --> 00:53:30.758
DYDINE UMUNYANA: Yeah,
it's really complicated.

00:53:30.758 --> 00:53:36.370
It's not perfect, but
at least it's not 1994.

00:53:36.370 --> 00:53:38.350
Yes, at least we're not there.

00:53:38.350 --> 00:53:40.660
